0her%20three%20kids%20in%20a%20mixed%20city%20in%20Israel.%20She%20makes%20sure%20the%20news%20is%20switched%20off%20when%20they%20come%20into%20the%20room.%3Cp%3EiStock%3B%20Rebecca%20Zisser%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeborah%20Danan%20and%20her%20husband%20are%20working%20parents%2C%20raising%20their%20three%20kids%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThey%20live%20in%20a%20mixed%20city%20where%20Jews%2C%20Muslims%2C%20and%20Christians%20live%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EShe's%20been%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20surprised%20by%20her%208-year-old's%20capacity%20for%20both%20compassion%20and%20comprehension%20of%20what%20was%20happening.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20learned%20surprising%20truths%20about%20my%20children%20since%20the%20horror%20of%20the%20October%207%20terror%20attack%20on%20Israel%20and%20the%20ensuing%20war%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fgaza%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGaza%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20with%20my%20husband%20and%20three%20kids%20in%20a%20mixed%20city%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fisrael%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIsrael%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20Jews%2C%20Muslims%2C%20and%20Christians%20live%20together.%20I%20moved%20here%20over%20a%20decade%20ago%20from%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJerusalem%2C%20while%20officially%20considered%20a%20mixed%20city%2C%20largely%20consists%20of%20religiously%20homogeneous%20neighborhoods%2C%20making%20apartment%20blocks%20with%20Jews%2C%20Muslims%2C%20and%20Christians%20living%20together%20%E2%80%94%20like%20mine%20%E2%80%94%20far%20less%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20the%20diversity%20in%20my%20city.%20I%20love%20that%20my%20children%20attend%20Christmas%20parades%20and%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20as%20I%20write%20this%20essay%20on%20a%20June%20afternoon%2C%20our