%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Darshan%20Shroff%2C%20a%20Mumbai-based%20wedding%20planner.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20to%20describe%20wedding%20planners%20in%20India%20as%20circus%20masters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2207e84198-c3b3-4ae5-b860-565eaa82e3bd%5C%22%3EPrivacy%20and%20security%20are%20top%20concerns%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20celebrity%20or%20influencer%20couples%20are%20particular%20about%20how%20their%20wedding%20is%20portrayed%20on%20the%20news%20and%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlanners%20have%20strict%20instructions%20that%20restrict%20posts%20from%20vendors%20about%20outfits%2C%20decor%2C%20or%20flowers%20before%20a%20set%20date.%20Most%20big%20weddings%20also%20collect%20the%20phones%20of%20their%20guests%20for%20privacy%2C%20and%20couples%20have%20teams%20that%20work%20with%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20have%20too%20many%20people%20hanging%20out%20taking%20their%20pictures.%20It%20makes%20them%20very%20uncomfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20Modgil%20said%20about%20celebrity%20guests%20and%20couples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETop%20security%20firms%20and%20even%20local%20authorities%20may%20sketch%20out%20safety%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20minute%20there%20are%20some%20kind%20of%20celebrities%2C%20whether%20it's%20politicians%20or%20Bollywood%2C%20security%20becomes%20very%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Modgil%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20had%20separate%20people%20escorting%20them%20and%20even%20taking%20them%20back%20because%20sometimes%20they%20even%20get%20mobbed.%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20families%20and%20their%20guests%20are%20not%20always%20easy%20to%20please.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAggarwal%20said%20she%20has%20planned%20weddings%20where%20celebrity%20attendees%20call%20to%20confirm%20what%20type%20of%20hotel%20suite%20they%20will%20be%20staying%20in%20and%20what%20kind%20of%20car%20is%20coming%20to%20pick%20them%20up.%20Everything%20must%20match%20their%20lifestyle%20standard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f2b6f12d-16c9-4226-9b64-e59a5aa60374%5C%22%3ESetting%20a%20blueprint%20for%20other%20weddings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ambani%20wedding%20is%20already%20influencing%20how%20other%20Indians%20are%20envisioning%20and%20planning%20their%20own%20nuptials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20planners%20told%20BI%20that%20brides%20are%20asking%20them%20for%20the%20same%20designers%20that%20Radhika%20Merchant%20wore%20in%20her%20pre-wedding%20events%2C%20like%20the%20custom%20lehengas%20designed%20by%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3EAbu%20Jani%20Sandeep%20Khosla%20and%20Tarun%20Tahiliani.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Radhika%20Merchant%20wore%20a%20Swarovski%20crystal%20lehenga%20designed%20by%20Abu%20Jani%20and%20Sandeep%20Khosla%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668e3264b2528216eeb4feaa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22691%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERadhika%20Merchant%20wore%20a%20Swarovski%20crystal%20lehenga%20designed%20by%20Abu%20Jani%20and%20Sandeep%20Khosla.%3Cp%3EAshish%20Vaishnav%20via%20Getty%20Image%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPlanners%20expect%20the%20main%20wedding%20to%20leave%20an%20even%20bigger%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20immense%20influence%20celebrities%20have%2C%20their%20weddings%20often%20become%20blueprints%20for%20future%20celebrations%20worldwide%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bharat%20Jagasia%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20wedding%20planner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20Ambani%20wedding%2C%20I%20am%20particularly%20excited%20to%20see%20how%20they%20differentiate%20the%20main%20event%20from%20their%20pre-wedding%20functions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20festivities%20are%20slated%20to%20kick%20off%20Friday%20at%20the%20Jio%20World%20Convention%20Centre%2C%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20Ambani%20family.%20It%20can%20accommodate%20over%2016%2C000%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20o