%20which%20it%20has%20called%20an%20%26quot%3BOff-Board%20Sensing%20Station%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20OBSS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CCA%20program%20redefines%20the%20future%20of%20aviation%20and%20will%20shape%20the%20USAF%20acquisition%20model%20to%20deliver%20affordable%20combat%20mass%20to%20the%20warfighter%20at%20the%20speed%20of%20relevancy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mike%20Atwood%2C%20the%20company's%20vice%20president%20of%20Advanced%20Programs%2C%20said%20in%20an%20announcement%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20release%20of%20the%20previously%20unseen%20first%20flight%20footage%20on%20June%2026%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20Research%20Lab%20(AFRL)%20awarded%20GA-ASI%20a%20new%20%249.3%20million%20contract%20for%20additional%20research%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20bringing%20AFRL's%20investment%20on%20the%20XQ-67A%20up%20to%20nearly%20%2468%20million.%20And%2C%20in%20an%20exclusive%20report%20published%20July%206%2C%20Air%20and%20Space%20Forces%20Magazine%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airandspaceforces.com%2Fcca-contract-expected-fall-first-version-under-construction%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20first%20contract%20for%20delivery%20of%20CCA%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20awarded%20to%20one%20or%20both%20contractors%20this%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20XQ-67A%20takes%20its%20maiden%20flight.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6690542a5439fb59cebcb82a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22594%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20XQ-67A%20takes%20its%20maiden%20flight.%3Cp%3EAir%20Force%20Research%20Laboratory%2FDVIDs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20angles%20highlighted%20in%20the%20short%20video%20underscore%20the%20unique%20design%20of%20this%20prospective%20fighter%20jet%20teammate.%20Like%20a%20fighter%2C%20it%20has%20a%20pair%20of%20angled%20vertical%20stabilizers%2C%20a%20large%20jet%20intake%20%E2%80%94%20in%20this%20case%20where%20the%20cockpit%20would%20be%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twz.com%2Fair%2Fthe-xq-67a-has-a-secretive-higher-performance-deadly-cousin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20War%20Zone%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20pointed%20out%2C%20what%20look%20like%20openings%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usgs.gov%2Fcenters%2Feros%2Fscience%2Fusgs-eros-archive-aerial-photography-side-looking-airborne-radar-slar-mosaics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eside-looking%20airborne%20radar%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Based%20on%20the%20taxi%20shots%2C%20the%20aircraft%20appears%20to%20be%20similar%20in%20size%20to%20a%20small%20private%20plane%20such%20as%20the%20Cessna%20Skyhawk.%20And%20like%20many%20aircraft%20in%20that%20category%2C%20it%20has%20fixed%2C%20rather%20than%20retractable%2C%20landing%20gear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unknowns%20for%20this%20CCA%20prototype%20remain%20abundant%2C%20including%20its%20top%20speed%2C%20range%2C%20and%20payload%20capacity.%20Also%20unclear%20is%20what%20that%20payload%20will%20ultimately%20consist%20of%2C%20and%20whether%20the%20OBSS%2C%20or%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twz.com%2Fair%2Fthe-xq-67a-has-a-secretive-higher-performance-deadly-cousin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evariant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20will%20be%20able%20to%20carry%20weapons.%20A%20payload%20that%20includes%20weapons%20has%20always%20been%20part%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airandspaceforces.com%2Farticle%2Fcollaborative-combat-aircraft-for-disruptive-air-warfare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAir%20Force's%20ultimate%20vision%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20CCA.%20Also%20unclear%20is%20to%20what%20extent%20the%20OBSS%2C%20which%20is%20remotely%20piloted%20but%20also%20capable%20of%20autonomous%20flight%2C%20employed%20autonomy%20in%20its%20maiden%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20announcement%20accompanying%20the%20new%20footage%2C%20Air%20and%20Space%20Forces%20Magazine%20hailed%20the%20rapid%20design%2C%20building%2C%20and%20testing%20process%20that%20led%20to%20a%20first%20flight%20in%20just%20over%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20to%20be%20built%20on%20a%20common%20chassis%20or%20genus%20%E2%80%94%20much%20like%20that%20of%20a%20motor%20vehicle%20frame%20%E2%80%94%20and%20with%20its%20first%20successful%20flight%2C%20the%20XQ-67A%20is%20proof%20that%20the%20genus%20approach%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20announcement%20stated.%20%26quot%3BThis%20enables%20a%20faster%20and%20more%20cost-effective%20replication%20of%20the%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20XQ-67A%20taxies%20down%20a%20runway.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669053db9caa6ed01e00f359%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22424%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20XQ-67A%20taxies%20down%20a%20runway.%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Atomics%20Aeronautical%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20OBSS%20shares%20much%20of%20its%20DNA%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fnews%2Famericas-ai-controlled-xq-58-valkyrie-flies-air-combat-exercises%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKratos%20XQ-58A%20Valkyrie%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20entrant%20in%20the%20Air%20Force's%20Skyborg%20program%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dvidshub.net%2Fnews%2F464915%2Fmarine-corps-xq-58a-valkyrie-completes-second-successful-flight%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremains%20in%20use%20by%20the%20Marine%20Corps%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20testbed%20platform.%20The%20Marine%20Corps%20anticipated%20the%20Valkyrie%20to%20meet%20a%20variety%20of%20needs%20ranging%20from%20electronic%20warfare%20to%20fires%20support%2C%20and%20as%20a%20platform%20to%20inform%20its%20own%20low-cost%20drone%20wingman%20program%2C%20the%20Penetrating%20Affordable%20Autonomous%20Collaborative%20Killer%2C%20or%20PAACK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20challenges%20remain%20ahead%20of%20OBSS%20as%20the%20Air%20Force%20continues%20to%20fast-track%20plans%20for%20its%20cheap%2C%20smart%20drone%20fleet%2C%20which%20it%20calls%20Low%20Cost%20Attritable%20Aircraft%20Technologies%2C%20or%20LCAAT.%20The%20Air%20Force%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airandspaceforces.com%2Fkendall-air-force-100-ccas-five-years%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efast-track%20production%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20first%20100%20collaborative%20combat%20aircraft%2C%20delivering%20them%20to%20the%20fleet%20by%202029.%20Ultimately%2C%20according%20to%20Air%20Force%20Secretary%20Frank%20Kendall%2C%20who%20testified%20before%20Congress%20this%20spring%2C%20the%20service%20wants%20at%20least%201%2C000%20and%20possibly%20as%20many%20as%202%2C000%20CCAs%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airandspaceforces.com%2Fkendall-air-force-100-ccas-five-years%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20an%20individual%20cost%20of%20%2430%20million%20or%20less%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20Force%20hopes%20CCA%20won't%20just%20augment%20or%20modernize%20air%20warfare%20%E2%80%94%20but%20transform%20it%20entirely.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmitchellaerospacepower.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FThe-Need-For-CCAs-for-Disruptive-Air-Warfare-FULL-FINAL.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20released%20in%20February%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Mitchell%20Institute%20for%20Aerospace%20Studies%20emphasizes%20that%20the%20service%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Boldes