ich%20she%20never%20learned%20in%20school.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Allison%20Nichol%20Longtin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-literacy-things-about-money-adults-dont-know-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NATO%20is%20taking%20greater%20control%20of%20Western%20efforts%20to%20back%20Ukraine's%20fight%20as%20US%20politics%20raise%20questions%20about%20its%20reliability%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225007%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20soldiers%20in%20dugouts%20firing%20mortar%20rounds.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66903e3e9caa6ed01e00ea3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223338%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20are%20fighting%20on%20the%20front%20lines%20with%20the%20support%20of%20Western%20partners%2C%20but%20there%20are%20questions%20about%20the%20reliability%20of%20those%20partnerships.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FEfrem%20Lukatsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPast%20political%20gridlocks%20and%20the%20upcoming%20US%20presidential%20election%20have%20fueled%20concerns%20over%20future%20Ukrainian%20military%20aid.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDonald%20Trump%2C%20a%20critic%20of%20NATO%2C%20has%20questioned%20the%20large%20amount%20of%20support%20the%20US%20gives%20Kyiv.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENATO%20has%20a%20new%20initiative%20underway%20to%20keep%20the%20assistance%20flowing%20over%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENATO%20is%20moving%20forward%20with%20a%20new%20initiative%20that%20will%20see%20it%20take%20greater%20control%20over%20Western%20efforts%20to%20arm%20and%20train%20Ukraine's%20military.%20The%20move%20comes%20as%20the%20alliance%20aims%20to%20solidify%20the%20long-term%20support%20for%20Kyiv%20as%20it%20battles%20the%20Russian%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20also%20comes%20as%20uncer