2Fit-is-easier-to-poach-big-tech-staff-now-says-intuit-ceo-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%20Sasan%20Goodarzi%3C%2Fa%3E%20added%20in%20the%20email%20that%20the%20company%20believes%20the%20staff%20would%20find%20more%20success%20elsewhere%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20Intuit%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20also%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20executive%20employees%20by%20about%2010%25%20and%20will%20cut%20300%20employees%20to%20%26quot%3Bstreamline%20work%20and%20reallocate%20resources%20toward%20key%20growth%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20email%20said.%20The%20tax-preparation%20software%20company%2C%20which%20offers%20products%20like%20Credit%20Karma%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturbotax-cant-advertise-as-free-when-many-pay-ftc-ruling-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETurboTax%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20moving%20forward%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Breorganization%26quot%3B%20plan%20to%20focus%20on%20these%20areas%2C%20according%20to%20the%20SEC%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20noted%20in%20the%20email%20that%20the%20cuts%20aren't%20a%20cost-reduction%20measure.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20hire%20a%20%26quot%3Bnearly%20equivalent%20number%20of%20employees%20in%20fiscal%202025%20%26quot%3B%20and%20expects%20its%20overall%20head%20count%20to%20grow%2C%20the%20filing%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20do%20layoffs%20to%20cut%20costs%2C%20and%20that%20remains%20true%20in%20this%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20Goodarzi%20said%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20key%20areas%20include%20its%20AI-powered%20assistant%20Intuit%20Assist%2C%20according%20to%20the%20filing.%20The%20CEO%20also%20stated%20plans%20to%20make%20investments%20in%20data%20and%20AI%2C%20accelerate%20money%20solutions%2C%20and%20expand%20its%20international%20growth%2C%20the%20filing%20detailed.%20The%20company%20is%20consolidating%2080%20tech%