0it's%20necessary%20to%20make%20the%20human%20species%20interplanetary%20in%20case%20of%20an%20extinction%20event%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpotentially-hazardous-asteroids-fly-by-earth-this-week-watch-live-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20asteroid%20impact%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Musk%20has%20also%20been%20waging%20a%20personal%20battle%20against%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpronatalism-elon-musk-simone-malcolm-collins-underpopulation-breeding-tech-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efears%20of%20underpopulation%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20has%20called%20%26quot%3Bthe%20biggest%20danger%20civilization%20faces%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20by%20fathering%20a%20lot%20of%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20had%2012%20known%20children%20with%20three%20different%20women%2C%20including%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-shivon-zilis-secret-twins-neuralink-tesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShivon%20Zilis%2C%20one%20of%20his%20top%20executives%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222150%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20and%20his%20son%2C%20X%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654d61333cc84b4dfaffcea5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20and%20his%20son%2C%20X%20%C3%86%20A-12.%3Cp%3ECristiano%20Barni%2FATPImages%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20only%20fitting%20that%20Musk%20might%20take%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-starship-flight-four-ocean-splashdown-elon-musk-plans-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emission%20to%20Mars%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20it's%20not%20yet%20clear%20whether%20human%20reproduction%20is%20possible%20on%20the%20red%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226fccabfd-0e50-48d9-b