NCLT%20directs%20grounded%20carrier%20Go%20First%20to%20release%204%20aircraft%20engines%20of%20ELF%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720722537000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F19%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1710832020-4701.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnclt-directs-grounded-carrier-go-first-to-release-4-aircraft-engines-of-elf-124071101272_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20NCLT%20has%20put%20the%20matter%20for%20further%20hearing%20on%20August%209%2C%20when%20other%20engine%20lessors%20may%20argue%20their%20case%20for%20return%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnclt-directs-grounded-carrier-go-first-to-release-4-aircraft-engines-of-elf-124071101272_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnclt-directs-grounded-carrier-go-first-to-release-4-aircraft-engines-of-elf-124071101272_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnclt-directs-grounded-carrier-go-first-to-release-4-aircraft-engines-of-elf-124071101272_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2211%20MLC%20Seats%2C%2012%20In%20Fray%3A%20Maharashtra%20Parties%20Move%20MLAs%20To%205-Star%20Hotels%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EResort%20politics%20has%20made%20a%20comeback%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20so%20has%20the%20possibility%20of%20cross-voting%20and%20horsetrading%2C%20as%20the%20state%20gears%20up%20to%20hold%20elections%20for%2011%20Legislative%20Council%20seats%20on%20Friday.%20Riding%20high%20after%20its%20unexpectedly%20good%20performance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20in%20which%20it%20won%2030%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20seats%2C%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20has%20fielded%20three%20candidates%2C%20one%20more%20than%20it%20has%20the%20numbers%20to%20elect%2C%20necessitating%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%2C%20which%20has%20288%20seats%2C%20currently%20has%20274%20members%2C%20meaning%20that%20every%20MLC%20candidate%20needs%2023%20first-preference%20votes%20to%20get%20elected.%20The%20ruling%20Mahayuti%20-%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20NDA%20alliance%20-%20which%20consists%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20wing%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20has%20fielded%20nine%20candidates%20and%20has%20201%20MLAs%2C%20including%20Independents%20and%20smaller%20parties%2C%20backing%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%2C%20which%20is%20under%20the%20INDIA%20umbrella%2C%20has%20the%20Congress%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20and%20the%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20as%20its%20key%20constituents%20and%20has%20put%20up%20three%20candidates%20despite%20having%20the%20support%20of%20only%2067%20MLAs.%20Six%20MLAs%2C%20including%20an%20independent%2C%20are%20neutral%20and%20may%20end%20up%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20elections%20because%2012%20candidates%20are%20now%20vying%20for%2011%20MLC%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20the%20exercise%20interesting%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20numbers%20game%2C%20is%20its%20timing%20-%20just%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20state%20-%20which%20has%20led%20to%20it%20being%20dubbed%20a%20semi-final.%20This%20is%20also%20only%20the%20second%20time%20that%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Maharashtra's%20unique%20political%20environment%2C%20where%20the%20split%20of%20two%20regional%20parties%20has%20led%20to%20two%20Shiv%20Senas%20and%20two%20NCPs%20-%20under%20very%20similar%20but%20different%20names%20-%20being%20pitted%20against%20each%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20were%20the%20first%20round%20and%20parties%20from%20both%20sides%20are%20now%20pulling%20out%20all%20stops%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20come%20out%20tops%20in%20the%20second.%20After%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20won%20just%20one%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20strong%20buzz%20that%20MLAs%20from%20his%20party%20are%20looking%20to%20jump%20ship%20and%20return%20to%20the%20faction%20of%20the%20party%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar.%20Their%20support%20is%20what%20may%20have%20given%20the%20opposition%20the%20confidence%20to%20field%20a%20third%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20who%20triggered%20the%20need%20for%20the%20election%20by%20fielding%20his%20close%20aide%2C%20Milind%20Narvekar%2C%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20not%20be%20doing%20it%20(fielding%20a%20third%20candidate)%20if%20we%20had%20not%20been%20confident%20of%20winning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20Numbers%20Stack%20Up%20-%20Mahayuti%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20103%20MLAs%2C%20has%20fielded%20five%20candidates%20-%20Pankaja%20Munde%2C%20Yogesh%20Tilekar%2C%20Parinay%20Phuke%2C%20Amit%20Gorkhe%20and%20Sadabhau%20Khot%20-%20which%20means%20that%20it%20is%2012%20MLAs%20short%20of%20the%20number%20it%20needs%20to%20get%20them%20elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20has%2037%20members%20in%20the%20Assembly%20and%20has%20put%20up%20two%20candidates%20-%20Krupal%20Tumane%20and%20Bhawana%20Gawli.%20It%20is%20nine%20MLAs%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar%20has%2039%20MLAs%20and%20has%20two%20candidates%20in%20the%20fray%2C%20%C2%A0Rajesh%20Vitekar%20and%20Shivajirao%20Garje%2C%20falling%20seven%20short%20of%20the%2046%20votes%20needed%20to%20get%20them%20elected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20coalition%20is%2C%20however%2C%20banking%20on%20nine%20MLAs%20from%20smaller%20parties%20and%2013%20Independents%20to%20see%20it%20through.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20Numbers%20Stack%20Up%20-%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20with%2037%20MLAs%20and%20one%20candidate%2C%20Pradyna%20Satav%2C%20is%20the%20only%20party%20with%2014%20surplus%20votes.%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%2C%20with%20its%2013%20MLAs%2C%20is%20supporting%20the%20Peasants%20and%20Workers%20Party%20(PWP's)%20Jayant%20Patil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chief%20minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Shiv%20Sena%20has%20put%20up%20Mr%20Narve%20as%20a%20candidate%20despite%20having%20just%2015%20MLAs%2C%20eight%20short%20of%20the%20figure%20it%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20votes%20may%20make%20up%20for%20the%20shortfall%20faced%20by%20Mr%20Patil%20and%20Mr%20Narve%2C%20but%20the%20votes%20of%20the%20AIMIM's%20two%20MLAs%2C%20the%20SP's%20two%2C%20the%20CPI(M)'s%20lone%20MLA%20and%20one%20Independent%20-%20all%20of%20whom%20are%20seen%20to%20be%20neutral%20-%20will%20be%20key.%20The%20Congress%20has%20claimed%20the%20coalition%20has%20the%20support%20of%20at%20least%20some%20of%20these%20MLAs%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMLAs%20In%20Hotels%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20Vijay%20Wadettiwar%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20organised%20a%20dinner%20meeting%20for%20his%20party%20MLAs%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Thursday%20night.%20The%20Congress%20has%20issued%20a%20whip%20to%20its%20MLAs%20asking%20them%20to%20vote%20for%20candidates%20of%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi.%20Exact%20instructions%2C%20given%20the%20surplus%20votes%2C%20will%20be%20issued%20just%20before%20voting%20begins%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUddhav%20Thackeray%20held%20a%20dinner%20interaction%20with%20his%20MLAs%20at%20a%20five-star%20hotel%20in%20central%20Mumbai%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%20All%2011%20MLAs%20who%20attended%20the%20meeting%20stayed%20back%20at%20the%20hotel%2C%20where%20the%20four%20remaining%20legislators%20joined%20them%20on%20Thursday%2C%20said%20a%20party%20leader.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20has%20moved%20its%20MLAs%20to%20a%20five-star%20hotel%20near%20the%20airport%20in%20suburban%20Mumbai%20while%20MLAs%20from%20Shiv%20Sena%20gathered%20in%20Vidhan%20Bhavan%20complex%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20for%20a%20meeting%20and%20then%20moved%20to%20a%20five-star%20hotel%20in%20Bandra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MLAs%20are%20also%20at%20a%20luxury%20hotel%2C%20but%20the%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20has%20not%20made%20any%20such%20move.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayant%20Patil%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20president%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20full%20faith%20in%20our%20MLAs%20and%20don't%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20keep%20them%20in%20five-star%20hotels.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20will%20take%20place%20from%209%20am%20to%204%20pm%20and%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20begin%20an%20hour%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20PTI)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720722060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F9ko7rkcg_devendra-fadnavis-eknath-shinde-ajit-pawar-fadanvis-shinde-ajit_625x300_11_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F11-mlc-seats-12-names-maharashtra-gears-up-for-assembly-poll-semi-finals-6085284%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Resort%20politics%20has%20made%20a%20comeback%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20as%20has%20the%20possibility%20of%20cross-voting%20and%20horsetrading%2C%20as%20the%20state%20gears%20up%20to%20hold%20elections%20for%2011%20Legislative%20Council%20seats%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F11-mlc-seats-12-names-maharashtra-gears-up-for-assembly