%20the%20Jaipur%20airport.%20The%20incident%20was%20caught%20on%20a%20CCTV%20camera%20at%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CISF%20officials%2C%20Anuradha%20Rani%20was%20stopped%20by%20assistant%20sub%20inspector%20Giriraj%20Prasad%20over%20not%20having%20valid%20permission%20to%20enter%20through%20a%20gate%20while%20she%20was%20entering%20the%20airport%20with%20other%20staff%20members%20around%204%20am.%20Ms%20Anuradha%20was%20then%20asked%20to%C2%A0undergo%20screening%C2%A0for%20airline%20crew%20at%20a%20nearby%20entrance%20but%20no%20female%20CISF%20personnel%20was%20present%20there%20at%20the%20time%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assistant%20sub%20inspector%20then%20called%20for%20a%20female%20colleague%20to%20complete%20the%20security%20check%20but%20an%20argument%20had%20already%20escalated%20by%20then%20which%20ended%20with%20the%20female%20employee%20slapping%20the%20assistant%20sub%20inspector%2C%20said%C2%A0Jaipur%20airport%20station%20house%20officer%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3ERam%20Lal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20official%20statement%20by%20a%C2%A0SpiceJet%20spokesperson%2C%20the%20employee%20had%C2%A0a%20%26quot%3Bvalid%20airport%20entry%20pass%26quot%3B.%20The%20company%20has%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20female%20employee%20was%20%26quot%3Bsubjected%20to%20inappropriate%20and%20unacceptable%20language%20by%20the%20CISF%20personnel%2C%20including%20asking%20her%20to%20come%20and%20meet%20him%20after%20his%20duty%20hours%20at%20his%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20an%20unfortunate%20incident%20occurred%20at%20Jaipur%20Airport%20involving%20a%20SpiceJet%20female%20security%20staff%20member%20and%20a%20male%20CISF%20personnel.%20While%20escorting%20a%20catering%20vehicle%20at%20the%20steel%20gate%2C%20our%20female%20security%20staff%20member%2C%20who%20had%20a%20valid%20airport%20entry%20pass%20issued%20by%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20Security%20(BCAS)%2C%20India's%20civil%