r%20Sullivan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NSA%2C%20however%2C%20acknowledged%20that%20countries%20like%20India%20have%20a%20historic%20relationship%20with%20Russia%20and%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20change%20dramatically%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20playing%20the%20long%20game.%20It%20(US)%20is%20making%20investments%20in%20democratic%20partners%20and%20allies%20around%20the%20world%20including%20countries%20like%20India%20and%20we%20think%20that%20that%20will%20pay%20off%20as%20we%20go%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20came%20a%20day%20after%20spokespersons%20of%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20the%20White%20House%20and%20the%20State%20Department%20reacted%20separately%20to%20questions%20on%20India's%20relationship%20with%20Russia%20and%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20was%20in%20Russia%20for%20two%20days%20for%20the%2022nd%20India-Russia%20annual%20summit%20that%20has%20been%20watched%20closely%20by%20the%20West%20amidst%20the%20raging%20Ukraine%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20talks%20with%20Mr%20Putin%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20told%20the%20Russian%20President%20that%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20is%20not%20possible%20on%20the%20battlefield%20and%20peace%20efforts%20do%20not%20succeed%20amid%20bombs%20and%20bullets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20stoutly%20defending%20its%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20and%20privileged%20strategic%20partnership%26quot%3B%20with%20Russia%20and%20maintained%20the%20momentum%20in%20the%20ties%20notwithstanding%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20not%20yet%20condemned%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%202022%20and%20has%20consistently%20pitched%20for%20a%20resolution%20of%20the%20conflict%20through%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20