dia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2F6-5-magnitude-earthquake-jolts-canada%2Famp_articleshow%2F111667905.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20%26quot%3BNon-Creamy%20Layer%26quot%3B%20And%20Rs%2022%20Crore%20Assets%3F%20The%20Puja%20Khedkar%20Story%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETrainee%20IAS%20officer%20Puja%20Khedkar%2C%20caught%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20massive%20controversy%20over%20claims%20she%20made%20in%20her%20UPSC%20candidature%2C%20has%20properties%20worth%20crores%2C%20NDTV%20has%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ms%20Khedkar's%20%26quot%3Bstatement%20of%20immovable%20property%20for%20the%20year%202023%26quot%3B%2C%20updated%20as%20of%20January%201%2C%202024%2C%20and%20exclusively%20accessed%20by%20NDTV%2C%20the%20junior%20officer%20owns%20five%20plots%20of%20land%20and%20two%20apartments%20across%20Maharashtra.%20The%20value%20of%20these%20assets%20totals%20a%20whopping%20Rs%2022%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F00tpvc9g_puja-khedkar-assets-ndtv_625x300_11_July_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disclosure%20lists%20her%20as%20the%20owner%20of%20two%20plots%20of%20land%20in%20Pune%20district's%20Mahalunge%20worth%20nearly%20Rs%2016%20crore%2C%20one%20in%20Pune%20district's%20Dhadawali%20worth%20Rs%204%20crore%2C%20and%20two%20in%20Ahmednagar's%20Pachunde%20and%20Nandur%20worth%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20and%20Rs%201%20crore%20respectively.%20The%20plots%20in%20Pachunde%20and%20Nandur%20were%20a%20gift%20from%20her%20mother.%20In%20all%2C%20she%20owns%20over%2022%20acres%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20has%20two%20apartments%20in%20Ahmednagar%20and%20Pune.%20The%20984-square-foot%20flat%20in%20Ahmednagar's%20Savedi%20is%20worth%20Rs%2045%20lakh%20and%20the%20724-square-foot%20apartment%20in%20Pune's%20Kondhwa%20is%20worth%20Rs%2075%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20assets%20were%20acquired%20between%202014%20and%202019%20and%20Ms%20Khedkar%20earns%20Rs%2042%20lakh%20annually%20from%20them.%20Moreover%2C%20according%20to%20Vijay%20Kumbhar%2C%20an%20RTI%20activist%20from%20Pune%2C%20her%20father%20has%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2040%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khedkar%20posed%20as%20an%20OBC%20non-creamy%20layer%20candidate%20in%20her%20UPSC%20candidature.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20to%20qualify%20as%20an%20OBC%20non-creamy%20layer%20candidate%2C%20the%20annual%20income%20of%20the%20applicant's%20parents%20or%20the%20yearly%20income%20of%20the%20family%20should%20not%20be%20more%20than%20Rs%208%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khedkar%2C%20who%20had%20an%20all-India%20rank%20of%20841%2C%20also%20claimed%20visual%20and%20mental%20disability.%20However%2C%20she%20did%20not%20undergo%20the%20mandatory%20medical%20tests%20to%20corroborate%20her%20disability%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20mounting%20trouble%20for%20the%20new%20IAS%20officer%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20formed%20a%20single-member%20panel%20to%20verify%20the%20%26quot%3Bcandidature%20claims%20and%20other%20details%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20submitted.%20The%20committee%20will%20submit%20its%20report%20in%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202023-batch%20IAS%20officer%2C%20currently%20on%2024-month%20probation%2C%C2%A0is%20facing%20serious%20charges%20of%20impropriety%20and%20%26quot%3Babuse%20of%20power%26quot%3B.%20It%20is%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20using%20a%20red-blue%20beacon%2C%20VIP%20number%20plates%2C%20and%20a%20%26quot%3BGovernment%20of%20Maharashtra%26quot%3B%20sticker%20on%20her%20private%20vehicle%2C%20an%20Audi%20sedan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20escalating%20row%2C%20Ms%20Khedkar%20has%20been%20transferred%20to%20Washim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGovernment%20rules%20do%20not%20allow%20me%20to%20speak%20anything%20on%20this%20matter.%20So%20sorry%2C%20I%20cannot%20speak%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Khedkar%20told%20the%20media%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720714860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fvk5ojve8_puja-khedkar_625x300_10_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-non-creamy-layer-and-rs-22-crore-assets-the-puja-khedkar-story-6085237%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trainee%20IAS%20officer%20Puja%20Khedkar%2C%20caught%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20massive%20controversy%20over%20claims%20she%20made%20in%20her%20UPSC%20candidature%2C%20has%20properties%20worth%20crores%2C%20NDTV%20has%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-non-creamy-layer-and-rs-22-crore-assets-the-puja-khedkar-story-6085237%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-non-creamy-layer-and-rs-22-crore-assets-the-puja-khedkar-story-6085237%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-non-creamy-layer-and-rs-22-crore-assets-the-puja-khedkar-story-6085237%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Barron%20Trump%20has%20father's%20grin%3A%20Body%20language%20expert%20on%20his%20first%20rally%20appearance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720714578000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111667747%2Cimgsize-891024.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbarron-trump-has-fathers-grin-body-language-expert-on-his-first-rally-appearance%2Farticleshow%2F111667783.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111667783.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBarron%20Trump's%20confidence%20showed%20that%20he%20accepted%20his%20father's%20audience%20as%20his%20audience%20which%20also%20showed%20potential%20aspiration%20--%20not%20just%20loyalty%2C%20body%20language%20expert%20Judi%20James%20said%20noting%20that%20he%20was%20clearing%20enjoying%20the%20adulation%20that%20he%20received%20at%20his%20first%20appearance%20in%20a%20political%20campaign%20rally.%20His%20grin%20is%20like%20his%20father's%20and%20his%20thumbs-up%20was%20also%20very%20Trump-like%2C%20the%20expert%20noted.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbarron-trump-has-fathers-grin-body-language-expert-on-his-first-rally-appearance%2Farticleshow%2F111667783.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbarron-trump-has-fathers-grin-body-language-expert-on-his-first-rally-appearance%2Famp_articleshow%2F111667783.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbarron-trump-has-fathers-grin-body-language-expert-on-his-first-rally-appearance%2Famp_articleshow%2F111667783.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIn%20Pakistan%2C%20Kohli%20Will%20Forget%20The%20Love%20He%20Has%20Received%20In%20India%26quot%3B%3A%20Afridi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmidst%20reports%20of%20India's%20decision%20to%20refrain%20from%20travelling%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20next%20year's%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20former%20captain%20Shahid%20Afridi%20feels%20that%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20forget%20the%20love%20and%20affection%20he%20has%20received%20in%20India%20if%20he%20visits%20Pakistan.%20The%20veteran%20all-rounder%20asserted%20that%20Kohli%20has%20a%20huge%20number%20of%20admirers%20and%20gets%20massive%20adulation%20in%20Pakistan.%20Afridi%20also%20urged%20the%20Indian%20team%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%202025%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20keeping%20aside%20the%20difficult%20political%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20welcome%20the%20Indian%20team%20(in%20Pakistan)%20and%20they%20should%20come.%20We've%20always%20received%20huge%20respect%20and%20love%20in%20our%20tours%20of%20India.%20In%20the%20same%20way%2C%20the%20Indian%20team%20also%20received%20love%20and%20respect%20during%20their%20tour%20in%202005.%20Cricket%20tours%20should%20be%20kept%20aside%20from%20politics.%20There%20is%20no%20big%20politics%20than%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20playing%20against%20each%20other%20in%20their%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Afridi%20told%20News24%20Sports'%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVirat%20will%20forget%20the%20love%20he%20has%20received%20in%20India%20when%20he%20would%20play%20in%20Pakistan.%20He%20has%20a%20huge%20craze%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20our%20people%20like%20him%20very%20much.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20is%20my%20favourite%20player.%20He%20has%20his%20own%20class%20and%20he%20shouldn't%20have%20retired%20from%20T20Is%20as%20because%20of%20him%20T20I%20looked%20beautiful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20next%20big%20thing%20of%20Indian%20cricket%20alike%20legends%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sachin-tendulkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Kohli%2C%20Afridi%20said%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20replicate%20their%20success%20in%20international%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfridi%20further%20went%20on%20to%20laud%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20structure%20especially%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20for%20unearthing%20a%20plethora%20of%20domestic%20talents%20and%20creating%20a%20solid%20bench%20strength%20for%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIPL%20has%20created%20so%20much%20talent%20pool%20for%20India%20that%20they%20can%20make%20two%20teams%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20inconsistency%20in%20Pakistan%20cricket%20administration%2C%20Afridi%20said%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20Chairman%20should%20be%20appointed%20for%20a%20longer%20duration%20so%20that%20the%20captain%20gets%20a%20decent%20tenure%20in%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChairman%20should%20at%20least%20get%20three%20years%20so%20that%20Pakistan%20captain%20can%20remain%20for%202-3%20years%20at%20his%20post.%20With%20the%20change%20of%20chairman%2C%20other%20things%20should%20not%20be%20affected.%20If%20we%20work%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20merit%2C%20the%20results%20will%20come.%20(Sahi%20banda%20agar%20sahi%20kursi%20par%20baithe%20toh%20result%20khud%20aa%20jayenge)%20If%20the%20right%20person%20takes%20the%20right%20job%2C%20then%20the%20result%20will%20come%20automatically%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720714560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fdqidtja8_virat-kohli-afp_625x300_27_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fin-pakistan-virat-kohli-will-forget-the-love-he-has-received-in-india-shahid-afridi-6085098%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20international%20captain%20feels%20that%20Virat%20Kohli%20will%20forget%20the%20love%20and%20affection%20he%20has%20received%20in%20India%20if%20he%20visits%20Pakistan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fin-pakistan-virat-kohli-will-forget-the-love-he-has-r