A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fmass-stranding-of-more-than-70-pilot-whales-in-scotland%2Famp_articleshow%2F111667424.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Forms%20Panel%20To%20Probe%20Disability%20Claims%20Made%20By%20Trainee%20IAS%20Officer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20formed%20a%20committee%20to%20verify%20%26quot%3Bcandidature%20claims%20and%20other%20details%26quot%3B%20submitted%20by%20trainee%20IAS%20officer%20Puja%20Khedkar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20misusing%20disability%20and%20OBC%20quota%20to%20secure%20a%20position%20in%20the%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202023-batch%20trainee%20IAS%20officer%20is%20also%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20massive%20allegations%20of%20impropriety%20and%20misuse%20of%20her%20position%20as%20a%20bureaucrat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20single-member%20committee%20will%20submit%20its%20report%20in%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20central%20government%20has%20constituted%20a%20single-member%20committee%2C%20chaired%20by%20a%20senior%20officer%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20Additional%20Secretary%20to%20government%20of%20India%20to%20verify%20the%20candidature%20claims%20and%20other%20details%20of%20Ms.%20Puja%20Manorma%20Dilip%20Khedkar%2C%20a%20candidate%20of%20Civil%20Services%20Examination-2022%20and%20earlier%20CSEs.%20The%20committee%20will%20submit%20its%20report%20in%202%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20alleged%20that%20Ms%20Khedkar%2C%C2%A0who%20is%20on%20probation%20for%2024%20months%2C%20had%20been%20using%20a%20red-blue%20beacon%2C%20VIP%20number%20plates%20and%20a%20%26quot%3BGovernment%20of%20Maharashtra%26quot%3B%20sticker%20on%20her%20privately-owned%20Audi%20sedan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20exchanged%20multiple%20WhatsApp%20messages%20with%20the%20Pune%20Collector's%20office%20before%20her%20posting%20and%20demanded%20confirmation%20of%20her%20%26quot%3Bseating%20arrangement%20and%20vehicle%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20an%20escalating%20row%2C%20Ms%20Khedkar%20has%20been%20transferred%20to%20Washim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGovernment%20rules%20do%20not%20allow%20me%20to%20speak%20anything%20on%20this%20matter.%20So%20sorry%2C%20I%20cannot%20speak%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Khedkar%20responding%20to%20the%20media's%20queries%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20emerged%20that%20she%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20visually%20and%20mentally%20impaired%20candidate%20to%20seek%20concession%2C%20but%20did%20not%20undergo%20a%20mandatory%20medical%20test%20for%20confirmation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPune%20RTI%20activist%20Vijay%20Kumbhar%20also%20raised%20questions%20about%20Ms%20Khedkar's%20appointment%20alleging%20that%20she%20did%20not%20fall%20under%20the%20OBC%20non-creamy%20layer%20as%20her%20father%20had%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2040%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20per%20the%20rules%2C%20only%20those%20come%20under%20the%20OBC%20non-creme%20layer%20category%20whose%20parents%20are%20under%208%20lac%20per%20annum%20of%20income%2C%20but%20their%20income%20shows%20that%20it%20is%2040%20crore.%20Her%20parents%20contested%20the%20recent%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20all%20the%20property%20details%20are%20there%20in%20the%20affidavit%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kumbhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20raises%20the%20question%20of%20how%20Puja%20Khedkar%20could%20come%20under%20the%20OBC%20non-creamy%20layer%20category.%20A%20detailed%20investigation%20must%20be%20done%20on%20how%20she%20was%20appointed%20as%20an%20IAS%20officer%20in%20that%20category%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20ranked%20841%20in%20the%20all-India%20exam%20--%20an%20unimpressive%20rank.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20that%20recruits%20top%20civil%20servants%20had%20challenged%20her%20selection%2C%20and%20a%20tribunal%20ruled%20against