%26quot%3Bhanging%20on%20the%20wall%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20criteria%20set%20to%20NOK%20is%20not%20correct.%20I%20have%20also%20spoken%20to%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20about%20this.%20Anshuman's%20wife%20doesn't%20live%20with%20us%20now%2C%20the%20marriage%20was%20just%20five%20months%20old%20and%20there%20is%20no%20child.%20We%20only%20have%20a%20photo%20of%20our%20son%20hanging%20on%20the%20wall%20with%20a%20garland%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fpankajjilive%2Fstatus%2F1811319661381722205%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3ETV9%20Bharatvarsh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%20we%20want%20that%20the%20definition%20of%20NOK%20be%20fixed.%20It%20should%20be%20decided%20that%20if%20the%20wife%20of%20the%20martyr%20stays%20in%20the%20family%2C%20who%20has%20how%20much%20dependency%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Singh's%20mother%20said%20they%20want%20the%20government%20to%20revisit%20the%20NOK%20rules%20so%20that%20other%20parents%20don't%20have%20to%20suffer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20NOK%20rules%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20of%20kin%20rule%20to%20a%20person's%20closest%20relatives%20or%20legal%20representatives.%20The%20rules%20of%20the%20Army%20say%20that%20if%20something%20happens%20to%20a%20person%20in%20service%2C%20the%20ex-gratia%20amount%20is%20given%20to%20NOK.%20In%20simple%20language%2C%20it%20is%20just%20like%20a%20nominee%20in%20a%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20cadet%20or%20officer%20joins%20the%20Army%2C%20his%20parents%20or%20guardians'%20names%20are%20recorded%20in%20the%20NOK.%20When%20that%20cadet%20or%20officer%20gets%20married%2C%20under%20Army%20rules%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20person's%20spouse%20is%20recorded%20as%20the%20person's%20next%20of%20kin%20instead%20of%20the%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Singh%20was%20posted%20with%2026%20Punjab%20as%20a%20