tions-6080806%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIf%20No%20Paper%20Leak%2C%20Why%20Arrests%2C%20And%20Other%20Big%20Questions%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcbi-arrests-2-more-including-a-candidate-in-neet-paper-leak-case-6069251%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELast%20week%20a%20student%20was%20arrested%20from%20Patna%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%2C%20excluding%20Rocky%2C%20arrested%20eight%20people%20in%20connection%20with%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETasked%20with%20investigating%20the%20nation-wide%20exam%20paper%20racket%2C%20the%20agency%20has%20so%20far%20filed%20six%20FIRs%2C%20or%20first%20information%20reports%2C%20including%20five%20for%20three%20separate%20cases%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20CBI%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20the%20NEET%20paper%20leak%20may%20have%20had%20its%20origins%20in%20the%20Hazaribagh%20school.%20Papers%20leaked%20from%20there%20also%20made%20their%20way%20to%20Bihar%2C%20a%20CBI%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-leak-hazaribagh-paper-leak-oasis-school-cbi-neet-ug-paper-leak-had-genesis-in-hazaribagh-zeroing-in-on-school-cbi-officials-6078152%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENEET-UG%20Paper%20Leak%20Had%20Genesis%20In%20Hazaribagh%3A%20CBI%20Officials%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%2C%20the%20CBI%20official%20said%20nine%20sets%20of%20papers%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20which%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20held%20on%20May%205%2C%20reached%20a%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20branch%20two%20days%20earlier%20for%20safekeeping.%20From%20there%2C%20two%20sets%20were%20transported%20to%20the%20Oasis%20School%20in%20Hazaribagh%2C%20which%20was%20a%20centre%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20and%20the%20seals%20on%20them%20were%20broken%20by%20the%20time%20they%20reached%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgency%20sources%20said%20Rocky%20was%20present%20when%20the%20question%20papers%20were%20unsealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20photos%20of%20the%20questions%20and%20shared%20them%20with%20'solver%20gangs'%2C%20the%20name%20given%20to%20an%20organised%20racket%20that%20provides%20answers%20to%20leaked%20papers.%20These%20were%20then%20shared%20with%20exam%20candidates%2C%20for%20prices%20running%20into%20the%20lakhs%2C%20who%20were%20trying%20to%20cheat.%20Rocky%20is%20also%20linked%20to%20another%20key%20figure%20in%20this%20racket%2C%20Sanjeev%20Mukhiya%2C%20who%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20this%20scam%20for%20two%20decades%20and%20is%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-who-is-sanjeev-mukhiya-the-alleged-mastermind-behind-neet-paper-leak-5963858%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWho%20is%20Sanjeev%20Mukhiya%3F%20Alleged%20Mastermind%20Of%20NEET%20Paper%20Leak%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrest%20of%20Ranjan%2C%20or%20Rocky%2C%20could%20bust%20the%20NEET%20case%20wide%20open%20even%20as%20the%20courts%20debate%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20leak%20of%20question%20papers.%C2%A0The%20government%20and%20the%20testing%20agencies%20both%20say%20the%20leak%20has%20been%20limited%20to%20localised%20regions%20and%20a%20few%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECBI%20sources%20said%20that%20while%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20exactly%20where%20the%20papers%20were%20leaked%20from%2C%20what%20the%20evidence%20points%20to%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20was%3A%20either%20from%20the%20bank%20branch%2C%20while%20in%20transit%20to%20the%20school%2C%20or%20from%20the%20school%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEET-UG%20exam%20is%20taken%20for%20admission%20to%20undergraduate%20medical%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EControversy%20-%20nearly%2024%20lakh%20students%20took%20the%20May%205%20exam%20-%20broke%20last%20month%20after%20results%20were%20declared.%20The%20first%20red%20flags%20were%20the%20unusually%20high%20number%20of%20perfect%20scores%3B%20a%20record%2067%20students%2C%20including%20six%20from%20one%20coaching%20centre%2C%20scored%20a%20maximum%20720.%20Questions%20were%20also%20asked%20over%20the%20award%20of%20'grace%20marks'%20-%20not%20exam%20protocol%2C%20the%20NTA%20said%20-%20to%201%2C563%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestions%20were%20also%20asked%20over%20the%20award%20of%20'grace%20marks'%20to%201%2C563%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20retest%20for%20those%20students%20was%20held%20last%20week%2C%20but%20hundreds%20did%20not%20appear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20row%20has%20made%20its%20way%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20had%20served%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20under-fire%20NTA%2C%20or%20National%20Testing%20Agency%2C%20which%20is%20the%20central%20body%20that%20conducts%20the%20NEET%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NTA%20today%20defended%20itself%20against%20claims%20the%20NEET%20paper%20had%20been%20leaked%20on%20popular%20messaging%20app%20Telegram%2C%20calling%20those%20images%20a%20%26quot%3Bfake%26quot%3B.%20In%20an%20affidavit%20filed%20on%20Wednesday%20the%20NTA%20said%20the%20screenshots%20shared%20on%20Telegram%20were%20%26quot%3Bfabricated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-2024-paper-leak-on-telegram-timestamp-was-manipulated-exam-body-on-fake-paper-video-6080860%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BManipulated%26quot%3B%3A%20Exam%20Body%20On%20%26quot%3BFake%26quot%3B%20NEET%20Paper%20On%20Telegram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NTA%20also%20claimed%20no%20NEET-UG%20question%20paper%20was%20found%20to%20be%20missing%2C%20and%20that%20no%20locks%20(of%20boxes%20containing%20the%20papers)%20were%20broken%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.co