%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Frj3c3mfo_modi-moscow_625x300_11_July_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20stance%20on%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20is%20well-established%3A%20it%20advocates%20for%20a%20cessation%20of%20hostilities%20and%20prefers%20dialogue%20over%20conflict%2C%20a%20position%20consistently%20articulated%20in%20international%20forums.%20However%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Moscow%2C%20his%20camaraderie%20with%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20and%20the%20pledge%20to%20enhance%20bilateral%20trade%20and%20defence%20cooperation%20signify%20a%20strategic%20shift%20in%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visit%20aims%20to%20send%20a%20strong%20message%20to%20India's%20Western%20allies%20that%20while%20navigating%20complex%20global%20issues%2C%20India%20remains%20committed%20to%20safeguarding%20its%20national%20interests.%20After%20all%2C%20India's%20Oil%20Marketing%20Companies%20(OMCs)%20saved%20over%20%2410%20billion%20from%20April%202022%20to%20May%202024%2C%20largely%20due%20to%20Russian%20crude%20imports%2C%20as%20per%20an%20analysis%20by%20the%20Indian%20Express.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20underscores%20India's%20enduring%20friendship%20with%20Russia%20amidst%20geopolitical%20dynamics%2C%20including%20a%20pointed%20message%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20has%20demonstrated%20adeptness%20in%20making%20bold%20foreign%20policy%20moves%2C%20exemplified%20by%20strong%20ties%20fostered%20with%20Gulf%20countries%20during%20his%20tenure.%20While%20India%20values%20its%20friendships%20with%20the%20US%20and%20other%20Western%20nations%2C%20it%20is%20steering%20its%20own%20course%20to%20protect%20its%20national%20interests.%20This%20is%20a%20trajectory%20which%20is%20set%20to%20accelerate%20in%20Modi's%20third%20term.%20The%20agreement%20to%20establish%20Indo-Russian%20joint%20ventures%20for%20defence%20production%20and%20facilitating%20military%20exports%20to%20mutually%20agreed%20friendly%20nations%20exemplifies%20this%20forward-looking%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20Russian%20trip%2C%20Modi's%20subsequent%20visit%20to%20Austria%20marks%20India's%20Prime%20Minister's%20first%20official%20trip%20since%201983%2C%20illustrating%20a%20pattern%20of%20seeking%20new%20allies.%20This%20trend%20has%20been%20evident%20since%20Modi%20took%20office%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi's%20third%20term%20is%20distinct%20in%20its%20recent%20foreign%20policy%20decisions.%20From%20inviting%20all%20neighbouring%20countries%20except%20China%20and%20Pakistan%20to%20his%20swearing-in%20ceremony%2C%20to%20strategic%20engagements%20at%20the%20G-7%20summit%20in%20Italy%2C%20and%20now%20visits%20to%20Russia%20and%20Austria%2C%20Modi%20is%20making%20significant%20statements%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20Foreign%20policy%20remains%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20Modi%203.0's%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Mayank%20Mishra%20is%20Consulting%20Editor%20at%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720699500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F358fdi9_modi-moscow_625x300_11_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frussia-visit-an-emphatic-foreign-policy-statement-from-modi-3-0-6083426%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20inviting%20all%20neighbouring%20countries%20except%20China%20and%20Pakistan%20to%20his%20swearing-in%20ceremony%2C%20to%20strategic%20engagements%20at%20the%20G-7%20summit%20in%20Italy%2C%20and%20now%20visits%20to%20Russia%20and%20Austria%2C%20Modi%20is%20making%20significant%20statements%20