ring%20about%20certain%20ingredients%20and%20foods%20that%20are%20said%20to%20harm%20health.%20The%2046-year-old%20started%20myth-busting%20and%20explaining%20straightforward%20concepts%2C%20such%20as%20why%20it%E2%80%99s%20perfectly%20fine%20to%20use%20a%20microwave%20oven%20or%20air%20fryer%2C%20why%20storing%20food%20in%20the%20fridge%20is%20safe%2C%20and%20why%20variations%20in%20salt%20types%20don%E2%80%99t%20significantly%20impact%20your%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20characteristic%20wit%20and%20sass%20won%20over%20the%20internet%2C%20offering%20a%20dose%20of%20sanity%20and%20science%20in%20a%20space%20crowded%20by%20people%20looking%20for%20two-minute%20fame%20without%20substantiating%20their%20claims%20with%20facts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChemical%20engineering%20in%20a%20home%20lab%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%20progressive%20household%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Krish%20Ashok%20was%20encouraged%20by%20his%20father%20to%20experiment%20with%20various%20kinds%20of%20food%20outside%20the%20home.%20He%20began%20cooking%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20but%20his%20real%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F299901%2Fnri-chef-vijaya-kumar-semma-new-york-city-michelin-star-south-indian-restaurant%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejourney%20with%20cooking%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20when%20he%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20for%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFi-1-1720529288.gif%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Myth%20busting%20with%20Krish%20Ashok%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356117%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20moving%2C%20he%20meticulously%20wrote%20down%20recipes%20from%20his%20mother%2C%20grandmother%2C%20and%20other%20older%20women%20in%20the%20family.%20He%20found%20their%20way%20of%20sharing%20recipes%20fascinatingly%20different%20from%20cookbook%20methods.%20Their%20inherent%20knowledge%20of%20the%20science%20of%20cooking%2C%20without%20viewing%20it%20through%20a%20scientist%E2%80%99s%20or%20engineer%E2%80%99s%20lens%2C%20captivated%20Ashok%20and%20sparked%20his%20interest%20in%20food%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20original%20interest%20in%20food%20science%20happened%20when%20I%20recognised%20that%20the%20way%20my%20grandmother%20or%20grand-aunt%20thought%20about%20food%20was%20fundamentally%20different%20from%20how%20recipe%20books%20tended%20to%20think%20about%20it.%20It%20was%20evident%20that%20my%20grandmother%20was%20thinking%20about%20food%20as%20heuristics%20and%20algorithms%20and%20in%20a%20very%20scientific%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashok%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20when%20he%20referred%20to%20cookbooks%2C%20they%20missed%20out%20on%20this%20important%20tacit%20knowledge.%20%E2%80%9CCookbooks%20don%E2%80%99t%20tell%20you%20why%20you%20need%20to%20add%20two%20cups%20of%20water%20for%20rice.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20teach%20you%20how%20to%20adjust%20for%20more%20rice%20or%20how%20to%20find%20out%20if%20something%20is%20cooked.%20When%20is%20the%20right%20time%20to%20add%20salt%3F%20This%20practical%20knowledge%20by%20first-hand%20experience%20was%20missing%20in%20cookbooks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKrish-Ashok-2-1720615037.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Krish%20Ashok%20is%20the%20author%20of%20Masala%20Lab%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKrish-Ashok-2-1720615037.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKrish-Ashok-2-1