o%20this%20idea.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20Meditel%20took%20shape%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20stretch%20to%20say%20that%20the%20innovation%20has%20grown%20with%20Nikhil%3B%20the%20two%20have%20shared%20a%20parallel%20journey%2C%20as%20the%20idea%20transcended%20from%20being%20a%20PowerPoint%20presentation%20to%20a%20paper%20model%20to%20a%20basic%20prototype.%20From%20there%20it%20transformed%20into%20a%20full-blown%20electrical%20model%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20nuances%20Nikhil%20found%20himself%20explaining%20to%20none%20other%20than%20football%20legend%20David%20Beckham%20in%20November%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trajectory%20has%20been%20dream-like.%20And%20in%20a%20tete-a-tete%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Nikhil%20lets%20us%20in%20on%20the%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20first%20Meditel%20model%20that%20Nikhil%20built%20when%20he%20was%20in%20Class%207%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356097%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20Meditel%20model%20that%20Nikhil%20built%20when%20he%20was%20in%20Class%207%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Nikhil%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20just%20wanted%20to%20help%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20known%20fact%20that%20skipping%20one%E2%80%99s%20medicine%20dosage%20is%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20good%20health.%20But%20as%20Nikhil%20soon%20deduced%2C%20medication%20non-adherence%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20one-pronged%20problem.%20It%20had%20many%20facets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20come%20up%20with%20an%20alarm%20system%20that%20would%20alert%20people%20when%20they%20needed%20to%20take%20their%20pills.%20But%2C%20eventually%2C%20as%20I%20observed%20my%20grandmother%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20even%20when%20she%20did%20remember%2C%20but%20did%20not%20have%20water%20handy%2C%20she%20would%20put%20it%20off%20for%20later.%E2%80%9D%20This%20led%20to%20Nikhil%20integrating%20a%20reusable%20water%20bottle%20into%20the%20device%2C%20attached%20by%20velcro.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20component%20was%20the%20pill%20organiser%2C%20born%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20people%20who%20were%20prescribed%20multiple%20doses%20specific%20to%20their%20meal%20times.%20%E2%80%9CMeditel%20allows%20users%20to%20set%20up%20to%20six%20daily%20alarms%2C%20accommodating%20various%20medication%20schedules%20like%20pre%2Fpost%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20and%20dinner%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nikhil%20explains.%20Sourcing%20the%20parts%20and%20putting%20the%20device%20together%20was%20one%20thing%20but%20coding%20to%20get%20the%20alarm%20systems%20in%20place%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20challenge.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20essentially%20the%20first%20model%20I%20was%20ever%20building%20from%20scratch%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nikhil%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20became%20savvy%20with%20the%20arduino%20%E2%80%94%20an%20open-source%20coding%20board%20%E2%80%94%20that%20sends%20a%20signal%20to%20the%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20device%20to%20control%20their%20working.%E2%80%9D%20The%20journey%20was%20fraught%20with%20learning%20and%20spanned%20months%2C%20with%20Nikhil%20refining%20his%20coding%20skills%2C%20sharpening%20his%20technical%20palette%20and%20perfecting%20Meditel%20with%20each%20learning.%20He%20credits%20his%20parents%20for%20their%20support%20through%20these%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FF_YjhVca0AANDEO-1720527218.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nikhil%20was%20a%20panellist%20at%20the%20World%20Children's%20Day%20conference%20at%20New%20Delhi%20in%202023%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FF_YjhVca0AANDEO-1720527218.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FF_YjhVca0AANDEO-1720527218-300x158.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FF_YjhVca0AANDEO-1720527218-500x263.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FF_YjhVca0AANDEO-1720527218-768x404.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FF_YjhVca0AANDEO-1720527218-1536x808.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FF_YjhVca0AANDEO-1720527218-150x79.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356107%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22842%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENikhil%20was%20a%20panellist%20at%20the%20World%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Day%20conference%20at%20New%20Delhi%20in%202023%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Nikhil%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommending%20Nikhil%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20approach%2C%20his%20mentor%20Mukesh%20Bind%20shares%20how%20his%20journey%20with%20Nikhil%20began%20during%20the%20World%20Robot%20Olympiad%20(2019)%20where%20they%20met.%20%E2%80%9CFollowing%20the%20competition%2C%20Nikhil%20started%20learning%20robotics%20with%20me.%20It%20was%20during%20one%20of%20our%20sessions%20that%20he%20expressed%20his%20desire%20to%20make%20a%20device%20that%20would%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F312904%2Fdesigner-shreya-thakkar-innovates-wander-on-assist-smart-cane-for-the-elderly%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20his%20grandfather%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20medication.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Meditel%20was%20deemed%20complete%20by%20Nikhil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInvention-1720583517.gif%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356175%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeditel%E2%80%99s%20success%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20many%20accolades%20that%20line%20Nikhil%E2%80%99s%20shelves%20%E2%80%94%20second%20runners-up%20at%20the%20Jagran%20Josh%20Education%20Awards%20in%20the%20Robotics%20Category%20(April%202024)%3B%20winner%20of%20the%20INSPIRE%20Awards%20(2023)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20national-level%20science%20fair%20organised%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%3B%20one%20of%2050%20innovators%20at%20the%20National%20Children%20Innovation%20Challenge%20in%20partnership%20with%20UNICEF%20(2023)%2C%20a%20panellist%20at%20the%20World%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Day%20Conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%20(2023)%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20one%20that%20surpassed%20all%20of%20these%2C%20Nikhil%20says%2C%20was%20the%20recognition%20from%20UNICEF%20in%20November%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98One%20of%20the%20top%20three%20moments%20of%20my%20life%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn%E2%80%99t%20every%20odd%20day%20that%20you%20get%20to%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20the%20legend%20Beckham%20and%20relay%20your%20dreams%20to%20him.%20But%20Nikhil%20did.%20And%20he%20classifies%20this%20as%20his%20top-tier%20moment%3B%20one%20he%20does%20not%20take%20lightly.%20Retracing%20his%20steps%20leading%20up%20to%20it%2C%20he%20says%20it%20was%20fated.%20%E2%80%9CI%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20planned%20it.%20I%20never%20applied%20to%20UNICEF.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20applied%20to%20another%20competition%20hosted%20by%20the%20incubation%20centre%20of%20Gujarat%20University%2C%20who%20sent%20my%20project%20to%20UNICEF!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20you%20can%20imagine%20Nikhil%E2%80%99s%20astonishment%20when%20he%20got%20a%20call%20one%20day%20in%20October%202023%20from%20Sanyam%20Chhajed%2C%20programs%20manager%20at%20GUSEC%20(Gujarat%20University%20Startup%20and%20Entrepreneurship%20Council)%2C%20informing%20him%20about%20an%20exhibition%20where%20a%20few%20dignitaries%20would%20be%20present.%20One%20thing%20led%20to%20another%20and%20on%2013%20November%2C%202023%2C%20Nikhil%20was%20one%20of%20five%20chosen%20students%20from%20across%20India%20presenting%20his%20work%20to%20Beckham%2C%20UNICEF%20Goodwill%20Ambassador.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FfYoX20Hz8V8%3Fsi%3DbBW7gjsAVQPnu1P4%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGUSEC%20has%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20his%20journey%2C%20Nikhil%20points%20out%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20has%20received%20immense%20support%20from%20the%20team%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relation